WEBVTT

1
00:00:21.396 --> 00:00:31.720
Today you all have decided
to have the puja of Adi Shakti.

2
00:00:31.933 --> 00:00:39.652
There's a difference between doing
the puja of Kundalini Shakti

3
00:00:39.888 --> 00:00:43.590
or Adi Kundalini and Adi Shakti.

4
00:00:44.171 --> 00:00:51.623
The difference is like this:
on one side the Kundalini

5
00:00:51.841 --> 00:00:58.370
is reflected in you by Adi Kundalini;

6
00:00:58.429 --> 00:01:05.082
the second side is the power
of Adi Shakti which is Paramchaitanya.

7
00:01:05.229 --> 00:01:10.165
So in totality, if you see,
it has two sides.

8
00:01:10.265 --> 00:01:14.818
One is Her power as Paramchaitanya

9
00:01:14.858 --> 00:01:22.005
and also reflection in human beings
as Kundalini.

10
00:01:28.440 --> 00:01:37.448
The third work that Adi Shakti
had to do was to create this universe.

11
00:01:37.490 --> 00:01:42.209
To begin with, as you have seen
yesterday also,

12
00:01:42.293 --> 00:01:45.428
how the cosmos was created

13
00:01:45.538 --> 00:01:56.497
and then how this special planet
of Mother Earth was created.

14
00:01:56.571 --> 00:02:01.378
Now what I have told you
about Adam and Eve,

15
00:02:01.431 --> 00:02:10.187
we have found out, said by also John
in his Gnostics book.

16
00:02:10.271 --> 00:02:11.537
It's very surprising.

17
00:02:11.689 --> 00:02:15.168
They always told you
that Christ must have told you many things,

18
00:02:15.212 --> 00:02:17.377
but they are not in the Bible.

19
00:02:17.397 --> 00:02:26.250
So if you understand
that this Adi Shakti came as a serpent —

20
00:02:26.250 --> 00:02:29.625
the Adi Kundalini part of Her —

21
00:02:29.625 --> 00:02:38.706
and told the Adam and Eve,
especially Eve,

22
00:02:38.776 --> 00:02:49.639
that she should ask for the fruit
of knowledge to be eaten.

23
00:02:49.761 --> 00:02:53.821
The reason I gave you
is exactly written there,

24
00:02:53.931 --> 00:02:58.482
that the Mother power,
the feminine power,

25
00:02:58.527 --> 00:03:01.713
didn't want Her children
to live like animals

26
00:03:02.175 --> 00:03:06.038
without understanding what is
the knowledge of the higher realms,

27
00:03:06.193 --> 00:03:12.755
not giving them chance to rise higher
through their freedom

28
00:03:12.755 --> 00:03:19.534
and then to higher and higher awareness.

29
00:03:19.534 --> 00:03:22.705
It was the concern of the Mother.

30
00:03:22.720 --> 00:03:29.151
So there were two types of worlds created,

31
00:03:29.151 --> 00:03:33.682
one was a divine,
another one started evolving.

32
00:03:33.682 --> 00:03:39.069
To look at it,
looks like a very tremendous task,

33
00:03:39.113 --> 00:03:43.780
thousands and thousands, billions
and billions of years have passed

34
00:03:43.780 --> 00:03:49.003
for this kind of a work to be done,

35
00:03:49.003 --> 00:03:57.667
but, if you see, in modern age
we are going to the moon

36
00:04:00.351 --> 00:04:10.757
with such a small effort
and also with such a little time

37
00:04:10.760 --> 00:04:11.712
you reach there.

38
00:04:11.712 --> 00:04:15.227
Nobody could think
that we'll ever be there.

39
00:04:15.234 --> 00:04:20.180
All this happened through
the human brain.

40
00:04:20.180 --> 00:04:23.059
Now what is the human brain after all?

41
00:04:23.059 --> 00:04:29.904
Human brain is not at all
anywhere near the brain of the Virata,

42
00:04:29.919 --> 00:04:35.575
nor is this used fully.
It's not used fully.

43
00:04:35.575 --> 00:04:39.550
It's very little bit is used
by human beings

44
00:04:39.550 --> 00:04:43.316
by which they have achieved
this kind of flight to moon.

45
00:04:43.316 --> 00:04:45.810
Of course, there was no purpose in it.

46
00:04:45.810 --> 00:04:49.803
I don't know why they are doing it,
but they did it.

47
00:04:56.670 --> 00:05:02.115
So the whole nature was created by Her.

48
00:05:02.115 --> 00:05:04.953
Whatever you see today
around yourself

49
00:05:04.998 --> 00:05:10.714
is all created by Her,
is all Her work that is there.

50
00:05:10.714 --> 00:05:16.765
You'll be amazed, just now I said
I was going to wear a very heavy sari

51
00:05:16.765 --> 00:05:21.834
and I said, "It's very hot
so I had better change to a simpler sari."

52
00:05:21.834 --> 00:05:27.264
So I changed and when I came out,
I found it had become cooler.

53
00:05:27.264 --> 00:05:34.003
So the nature knows everything

54
00:05:34.003 --> 00:05:39.007
and who informs the nature
is this Paramchaitanya.

55
00:05:39.007 --> 00:05:42.150
Paramchaitanya was never that active.

56
00:05:42.150 --> 00:05:47.555
It started since My birth, I should say,
when Krita Yuga started.

57
00:05:47.555 --> 00:05:54.271
At this time, you had to have
your Realisation.

58
00:05:54.271 --> 00:05:59.529
That was decided
by the Divine Collectivity, you can call it.

59
00:05:59.630 --> 00:06:02.190
All the Gods, Goddesses, all of them

60
00:06:02.190 --> 00:06:10.897
decided to put this work on somebody
whom they thought to be very capable.

61
00:06:10.897 --> 00:06:16.438
So they said, "We all will be with you,
entirely with you.

62
00:06:16.438 --> 00:06:18.796
All our powers will be with you,

63
00:06:18.796 --> 00:06:23.298
but you take up this job now
in this Kali Yuga

64
00:06:23.298 --> 00:06:25.500
to transform human beings."

65
00:06:25.500 --> 00:06:30.926
In a way, human beings are more difficult
than animals

66
00:06:30.926 --> 00:06:34.269
because they have their own freedom

67
00:06:34.269 --> 00:06:40.672
and they have been given this freedom
to achieve their final freedom.

68
00:06:40.672 --> 00:06:46.628
In their freedom, the way they behave
is something very surprising,

69
00:06:46.628 --> 00:06:50.785
how they go completely out of control

70
00:06:50.785 --> 00:06:57.812
and try to do things
which are so destructive.

71
00:06:57.812 --> 00:07:01.713
Of course, in Kali Yuga
it was predicted in India

72
00:07:01.713 --> 00:07:05.223
but I think they could not predict
what would happen in America

73
00:07:05.223 --> 00:07:07.836
or what would happen
in the western countries

74
00:07:07.836 --> 00:07:12.004
where people have freedom
just to destroy themselves

75
00:07:12.004 --> 00:07:17.443
and they are finding new methods
of destroying themselves.

76
00:07:17.443 --> 00:07:25.504
This tendency cannot be curbed,
cannot be stopped

77
00:07:25.504 --> 00:07:29.283
by Adi Shakti or by God Almighty

78
00:07:29.283 --> 00:07:33.767
because you have been given
the freedom to ruin yourselves,

79
00:07:33.767 --> 00:07:36.760
spoil yourself
and to go to hell.

80
00:07:36.760 --> 00:07:40.970
That cannot be controlled
by any divine power.

81
00:07:40.970 --> 00:07:45.127
Divine power also respects your freedom.

82
00:07:45.127 --> 00:07:48.756
So the Divine Collectivity thought,

83
00:07:48.795 --> 00:07:56.749
"Are we going to completely ruin
the creation of Adi Shakti?

84
00:07:56.749 --> 00:08:05.360
Are we going to completely destroy
whatever She has created

85
00:08:05.360 --> 00:08:08.358
and then recreate something better?"

86
00:08:08.358 --> 00:08:11.413
This was the discussion going on

87
00:08:11.413 --> 00:08:16.763
and most of them were so fed up
with the human beings,

88
00:08:16.763 --> 00:08:19.360
especially with the western freedom,

89
00:08:19.360 --> 00:08:22.529
that they said,
"These people want hell

90
00:08:22.529 --> 00:08:29.812
and why should we give them the heavens?
It's not proper."

91
00:08:29.812 --> 00:08:38.493
So first thing Adi Shakti did
was to create a seeking in them.

92
00:08:38.493 --> 00:08:42.915
She created this desire to seek

93
00:08:42.915 --> 00:08:48.437
and so these people belonging
to this culture, which was so destructive,

94
00:08:48.437 --> 00:08:50.157
started seeking

95
00:08:50.157 --> 00:08:54.090
and when the seeking started also,
as usual,

96
00:08:54.090 --> 00:08:57.258
in the market there were many others
who came forward

97
00:08:57.258 --> 00:08:59.795
to give answers to their seekings.

98
00:08:59.795 --> 00:09:05.962
They had to go to various cults
and things and false people and all that

99
00:09:05.962 --> 00:09:08.714
because they had no way to know,

100
00:09:08.714 --> 00:09:14.839
but if they had read some books
of enlightened people

101
00:09:14.839 --> 00:09:24.795
like Kabir, like Nanak,
even Gnostics, their scriptures,

102
00:09:24.795 --> 00:09:25.913
anything like that,

103
00:09:25.918 --> 00:09:28.650
they would have understood
what is the truth

104
00:09:28.650 --> 00:09:32.490
and where to find it
and how to find it.

105
00:09:32.490 --> 00:09:38.751
It is a big struggle, I find,

106
00:09:38.751 --> 00:09:46.190
between the people who are seekers
and those who are not at all seekers.

107
00:09:46.190 --> 00:09:51.321
They don't want to know
and they can never be seekers.

108
00:09:51.321 --> 00:09:56.880
I can assure you
that some of them will never think of seeking.

109
00:09:56.880 --> 00:10:00.540
They'll get possessed,
they'll have diseases,

110
00:10:00.540 --> 00:10:06.454
they'll have earthquakes,
they'll have anything — they will never seek.

111
00:10:06.454 --> 00:10:11.941
Even if they get diseases, they'll say,
"Oh, we are martyrs.

112
00:10:11.941 --> 00:10:13.559
We are doing great work."

113
00:10:13.559 --> 00:10:18.278
Such stupidity has come into their heads

114
00:10:18.278 --> 00:10:23.999
that they think by doing
these wrong things we are going to be saved.

115
00:10:23.999 --> 00:10:30.974
And this stupidity comes through
the perverted brains

116
00:10:30.974 --> 00:10:37.316
and this perverted brain acts
when people are free to use it.

117
00:10:37.316 --> 00:10:40.305
I just don't know.
Why don't they see around

118
00:10:40.305 --> 00:10:43.267
and see for themselves
what is happening?

119
00:10:43.267 --> 00:10:46.829
So, to expect that the whole world
will go to heaven

120
00:10:46.829 --> 00:10:52.035
is absolutely not possible.
It's not possible. It cannot be.

121
00:10:52.035 --> 00:10:55.050
They have tried all kinds of things.

122
00:10:55.050 --> 00:11:00.676
I have seen people —
drugs and alcohol, this, that.

123
00:11:00.676 --> 00:11:03.635
There is one fellow who got his PhD

124
00:11:03.635 --> 00:11:08.101
on writing how he reached spirituality
through drinking

125
00:11:08.101 --> 00:11:10.609
and they gave him PhD for that.

126
00:11:10.609 --> 00:11:16.018
So even at the helm of affairs,
in the universities.

127
00:11:16.018 --> 00:11:20.362
I don't know how such stupid people
came up, from where,

128
00:11:20.362 --> 00:11:22.088
out of which creation.

129
00:11:22.088 --> 00:11:24.438
It's impossible to understand.

130
00:11:24.438 --> 00:11:29.815
How could they think
that this kind of destruction

131
00:11:29.815 --> 00:11:32.737
will lead them to their salvation?

132
00:11:32.737 --> 00:11:37.084
They see it every day.
They watch it every day.

133
00:11:37.084 --> 00:11:41.195
They know it is happening,
but still they cannot recede.

134
00:11:41.195 --> 00:11:47.376
But those who are seekers
are so ardently seeking

135
00:11:47.376 --> 00:11:51.522
that they will all have to be given
their Self-realisation.

136
00:11:51.522 --> 00:11:55.239
Now this is, of course, My job, I agree.

137
00:11:55.239 --> 00:12:00.451
I have come on this Earth for that job.
I am supposed to do it.

138
00:12:00.451 --> 00:12:02.310
I am trying My level best

139
00:12:02.910 --> 00:12:07.676
and no incarnation has lived
like I have lived for so many years.

140
00:12:07.676 --> 00:12:15.185
And such compassion of Mine
which really makes Me live,

141
00:12:15.185 --> 00:12:18.493
that I feel we have to have
many more Sahaja Yogis,

142
00:12:18.576 --> 00:12:24.705
we have to have big salvation.

143
00:12:24.705 --> 00:12:27.808
With that compassion and with that love,

144
00:12:27.808 --> 00:12:35.052
one can take to any measures, anything.

145
00:12:35.052 --> 00:12:40.181
I do not think those who are not seekers
will achieve it.

146
00:12:40.181 --> 00:12:43.949
Now why is it
some are seekers and some are not?

147
00:12:43.949 --> 00:12:45.954
One may say that.

148
00:12:45.954 --> 00:12:49.176
Adi Shakti, if She has created
all the human beings,

149
00:12:49.176 --> 00:12:51.957
all of them should have seeking.

150
00:12:51.957 --> 00:12:57.746
Because in freedom
they have lost their way.

151
00:12:57.746 --> 00:13:02.533
They are seeking something else
and they think they're right.

152
00:13:02.533 --> 00:13:04.853
They have a right to think
that they're right.

153
00:13:04.853 --> 00:13:09.083
Even a stupid fellow, even a mad person
thinks he's right.

154
00:13:09.083 --> 00:13:12.701
If you tell him that "You are mad,"
he will say, "You are mad."

155
00:13:12.701 --> 00:13:17.510
And this seeking,
though put into them,

156
00:13:17.510 --> 00:13:23.230
they are not yet capable,
so many of them,

157
00:13:23.230 --> 00:13:27.207
are achieving it in the proper way.

158
00:13:27.207 --> 00:13:32.140
Because for that one has to surrender,

159
00:13:32.140 --> 00:13:36.276
not one's freedom,
not one's intelligence,

160
00:13:36.276 --> 00:13:40.814
but the ego that has developed
in human beings.

161
00:13:40.814 --> 00:13:44.454
With this ego,
even I've seen people who are possessed,

162
00:13:44.454 --> 00:13:46.379
they want to keep the ego intact

163
00:13:46.379 --> 00:13:51.720
and, through the ego,
they want to use the possessions.

164
00:13:51.720 --> 00:13:53.578
Can you imagine?

165
00:13:53.578 --> 00:13:56.804
There are possessions of negative forces.

166
00:13:56.804 --> 00:14:03.604
Such people want to keep that intact

167
00:14:03.604 --> 00:14:07.920
so that they can use that
for their own purpose.

168
00:14:07.920 --> 00:14:12.783
They don't hate it.
They don't want to get rid of it,

169
00:14:12.783 --> 00:14:17.383
but they want to keep it
just because they can use these possessions

170
00:14:17.383 --> 00:14:18.659
for their use.

171
00:14:18.659 --> 00:14:23.801
So the category of seeking
is much less there.

172
00:14:23.801 --> 00:14:29.189
But there are many
who are nowhere near seeking,

173
00:14:29.189 --> 00:14:33.081
who are really, what we call them,
the evil people

174
00:14:33.081 --> 00:14:36.943
and they never want,
never never would want,

175
00:14:36.943 --> 00:14:38.633
that this world should change.

176
00:14:38.651 --> 00:14:42.389
Our media is dominated
by these evil people.

177
00:14:42.389 --> 00:14:44.486
They don't want world to change.

178
00:14:44.486 --> 00:14:47.226
They don't want to show anything
that is good.

179
00:14:47.226 --> 00:14:49.754
They don't want to see the point

180
00:14:49.754 --> 00:14:54.707
what is going to help,
what is benevolent for human beings.

181
00:14:54.707 --> 00:15:07.244
So on one side we see
such collective negativity.

182
00:15:07.244 --> 00:15:12.776
Another side we find seekers
who are real seekers.

183
00:15:12.776 --> 00:15:16.079
There are some who we can call
as half-baked

184
00:15:16.079 --> 00:15:18.765
and some are pseudo-seekers.

185
00:15:18.765 --> 00:15:27.483
If, in the name of seeking,
if they have done, we can say,

186
00:15:27.483 --> 00:15:31.610
some sort of a sacrifice,

187
00:15:31.610 --> 00:15:36.092
for them they are very great.

188
00:15:36.092 --> 00:15:43.703
Also, they get involved
with people who are claiming.

189
00:15:43.703 --> 00:15:49.351
Because I have never claimed anything,
they're not impressed by Me.

190
00:15:49.351 --> 00:15:51.097
I have not changed My dress.

191
00:15:51.097 --> 00:15:55.000
I live like a housewife,
so they are not impressed by Me.

192
00:15:55.000 --> 00:16:00.362
I have not developed two horns
to show something great about Myself,

193
00:16:00.362 --> 00:16:01.917
so they won't be impressed.

194
00:16:01.917 --> 00:16:07.815
But on the other side, if you see,
this is Maya, this is Mahamaya

195
00:16:07.815 --> 00:16:12.720
where Adi Shakti, you see,
does everything like human beings do —

196
00:16:12.720 --> 00:16:14.126
everything.

197
00:16:14.126 --> 00:16:18.312
You won't be able to find out
that She's divine.

198
00:16:18.312 --> 00:16:22.960
My family people could not find out
till I started this work,

199
00:16:22.960 --> 00:16:26.704
none of them except
for My father and mother.

200
00:16:26.704 --> 00:16:33.340
Nobody could find out
that I had any powers even.

201
00:16:33.340 --> 00:16:42.343
Such insensitivity to Divine
can be created by Mahamaya Power

202
00:16:42.343 --> 00:16:45.340
of Adi Shakti which is very important.

203
00:16:45.340 --> 00:16:49.977
Otherwise, you cannot judge,
you cannot understand.

204
00:16:49.977 --> 00:16:52.810
Despite that, I have many times
misjudged people

205
00:16:52.810 --> 00:17:02.379
because they know how to camouflage
for a little while, but then I discover.

206
00:17:02.379 --> 00:17:10.540
If the seeking is ardent
and they are seeking really the Truth,

207
00:17:10.540 --> 00:17:14.715
they will find it,
they will find it, no doubt

208
00:17:14.715 --> 00:17:18.065
because the whole creation
is for them.

209
00:17:18.065 --> 00:17:24.808
The whole universe is for them.
All deities are for them.

210
00:17:24.808 --> 00:17:31.456
All angels are for them.
They are all looking out for them.

211
00:17:31.456 --> 00:17:36.867
This is important
that we have so many Sahaja Yogis now.

212
00:17:36.867 --> 00:17:42.819
Nobody had so many Sahaja Yogis
in their lifetime

213
00:17:42.819 --> 00:17:47.325
because we have to have channels.

214
00:17:47.325 --> 00:17:53.086
I have to have channels
and these channels have to be very clean,

215
00:17:53.086 --> 00:17:59.882
have to be beautiful,
innocent and benevolent.

216
00:17:59.882 --> 00:18:07.023
If only they surrender to this fact,

217
00:18:07.023 --> 00:18:12.879
that we are here
as the instrument of God Almighty

218
00:18:12.879 --> 00:18:17.640
and that we have to give
benevolence to others.

219
00:18:17.640 --> 00:18:25.934
I tell you at least seventy percent
of work is done.

220
00:18:25.934 --> 00:18:32.427
But, even if they have got realisation,

221
00:18:32.427 --> 00:18:38.565
like a bird comes out of the shell,

222
00:18:38.565 --> 00:18:43.974
some of the birds still carry
the part of the egg

223
00:18:43.974 --> 00:18:49.783
and some of them are not even grown-up
to be birds.

224
00:18:49.783 --> 00:18:57.368
Now, we have to judge ourselves.
We have to understand ourselves.

225
00:18:57.368 --> 00:19:05.675
Another thing you know
that I'm a very mild person, very mild.

226
00:19:05.675 --> 00:19:08.388
People think I'm very forgiving.

227
00:19:08.388 --> 00:19:11.410
I know everyone,
not that I don't know,

228
00:19:11.410 --> 00:19:17.179
but I allow,
"All right, go ahead as far as you can go."

229
00:19:17.179 --> 00:19:23.006
Experience is the only way
a human being can understand, no doubt.

230
00:19:23.006 --> 00:19:25.656
If you tell him something
he will never understand.

231
00:19:25.656 --> 00:19:30.109
Experience of self-realisation
has made you understand,

232
00:19:30.109 --> 00:19:37.220
but again I would say
that we cannot give realisation

233
00:19:37.220 --> 00:19:39.253
to the whole world. We cannot.

234
00:19:39.253 --> 00:19:45.033
They are like stones,
absolutely horrible people.

235
00:19:45.033 --> 00:19:51.667
Whatever is happening is that
those who are false are getting exposed

236
00:19:51.667 --> 00:19:56.678
and everybody is noticing that,
that they are getting exposed.

237
00:19:56.678 --> 00:20:02.164
This exposure, of course,
will save them from these horrible people,

238
00:20:02.164 --> 00:20:04.837
but I don't know if they would come
to Sahaja Yoga

239
00:20:04.837 --> 00:20:08.303
or if they would take their Realisation.

240
00:20:08.303 --> 00:20:13.954
This I am telling you because,
now, I too have experience

241
00:20:13.954 --> 00:20:15.893
of human beings

242
00:20:15.893 --> 00:20:19.020
and all these years I have been working,

243
00:20:19.020 --> 00:20:25.340
I have seen that there are
people and people and people.

244
00:20:25.340 --> 00:20:34.943
Out of them the seekers
are extremely proud of their seeking.

245
00:20:34.943 --> 00:20:38.300
So some of them don't want
to give up their seeking.

246
00:20:38.300 --> 00:20:44.743
It's kind of a job,
you can call it a hobby.

247
00:20:44.743 --> 00:20:46.438
"We are seekers."

248
00:20:46.438 --> 00:20:50.065
Now, they have a certificate
of being a seeker.

249
00:20:50.065 --> 00:20:55.421
They will wear funny clothes,
have funny houses, funny hair, everything.

250
00:20:55.421 --> 00:21:00.549
Recluses, they could be,
aggressive, anything. "We are seekers."

251
00:21:00.549 --> 00:21:03.620
They take a certificate upon themselves,
"We are seekers."

252
00:21:03.620 --> 00:21:07.569
This is another quality
of seekers also.

253
00:21:07.569 --> 00:21:12.934
For them, it's a kind
of their lifestyle — "We are seekers." —

254
00:21:12.934 --> 00:21:17.502
and wherever they have to go,
they will go for seeking.

255
00:21:17.502 --> 00:21:20.096
They'll go to ten places
or twenty places.

256
00:21:20.096 --> 00:21:23.025
Every time they have argued with Me that,

257
00:21:23.025 --> 00:21:25.475
"Mother, there must be
some more ways of —"

258
00:21:25.475 --> 00:21:28.806
"Yes, maybe. I don't know of any.
You can go."

259
00:21:32.145 --> 00:21:39.835
Now, the main job of Adi Shakti today
is to give Realisation to people.

260
00:21:39.835 --> 00:21:41.742
That's my main job.

261
00:21:41.742 --> 00:21:47.207
All the rest is looked after,
is already managed, I should say,

262
00:21:47.207 --> 00:21:50.760
is like a computer.
I don't have to worry.

263
00:21:50.760 --> 00:21:55.527
It's a reflex action.
Whatever is happening is in a reflex action.

264
00:21:55.527 --> 00:21:58.473
I don't have to worry
about these things.

265
00:22:01.009 --> 00:22:05.687
Like people might say that,
"Mother, I prayed to You

266
00:22:05.687 --> 00:22:09.462
and how is it You help me so much?"

267
00:22:09.462 --> 00:22:11.260
It's all reflex action.

268
00:22:11.260 --> 00:22:15.015
At that time maybe that thought
may come to Me — thought —

269
00:22:15.015 --> 00:22:18.180
but it's a reflex action.
I really don't do anything.

270
00:22:18.180 --> 00:22:22.795
Actually, I am Nishkriya,
not doing anything whatsoever,

271
00:22:22.795 --> 00:22:26.398
the laziest person you could think of, Me.

272
00:22:29.734 --> 00:22:36.019
Really, because if there's a complete
organisation working for Me,

273
00:22:36.019 --> 00:22:41.523
why should I work? Nothing necessary.

274
00:22:41.523 --> 00:22:46.347
But one thing is there —
I'm witnessing

275
00:22:46.347 --> 00:22:54.675
and when I'm witnessing,
that acts on the reflex.

276
00:22:54.675 --> 00:22:58.695
That works out — the Paramchaitanya —

277
00:22:58.695 --> 00:23:02.815
because if that is the power
of the Adi Shakti,

278
00:23:02.815 --> 00:23:12.561
then whatever I witness
gets reported to that power.

279
00:23:12.561 --> 00:23:18.423
Is the other way round,
like see, we have electricity power somewhere.

280
00:23:18.423 --> 00:23:24.821
So, something goes wrong here,
it is not reflected to that power.

281
00:23:24.821 --> 00:23:29.433
It is not. Something goes wrong,
it finishes off here and here.

282
00:23:29.433 --> 00:23:35.664
But the other way round,
that if I witness something wrong,

283
00:23:35.664 --> 00:23:39.013
I don't have to do anything,
I'm just witness, I'm just watching.

284
00:23:39.860 --> 00:23:47.471
The whole thing acts through
this tremendous power of Paramchaitanya.

285
00:23:47.471 --> 00:23:52.391
Now this power you do not know.

286
00:23:52.391 --> 00:23:56.222
You know Kundalini.
You know all about chakras, this, that,

287
00:23:56.222 --> 00:24:09.785
but this power of Paramchaitanya
is in every particle, into every atom

288
00:24:09.785 --> 00:24:26.798
and it acts in such a manner
that it directs, it pushes you,

289
00:24:26.798 --> 00:24:32.808
it takes you to
the path of benevolence.

290
00:24:32.808 --> 00:24:37.112
Sometimes people say,
"Mother, I wanted to buy this shop.

291
00:24:37.112 --> 00:24:38.729
I couldn't get it, and all that."

292
00:24:38.729 --> 00:24:41.522
It is for your benevolence
you didn't get.

293
00:24:41.526 --> 00:24:48.901
Thank God. After ten days they'll come
and tell, "Thank God, I didn't get that."

294
00:24:48.901 --> 00:24:54.178
So gradually through experience,
you start understanding

295
00:24:54.178 --> 00:24:56.847
that we don't have to worry.

296
00:24:56.847 --> 00:25:01.949
If you are lost on the way,
normally people get very upset,

297
00:25:01.949 --> 00:25:03.445
but Sahaja Yogis don't.

298
00:25:03.445 --> 00:25:06.219
"Oh, very nice.
Must be something here

299
00:25:06.219 --> 00:25:08.651
that God has brought us here."

300
00:25:08.651 --> 00:25:14.653
This action slightly then changes.

301
00:25:14.658 --> 00:25:21.771
I would say the person
who is overactive starts thinking,

302
00:25:21.771 --> 00:25:27.952
"Now surrender. Islam. Surrender.

303
00:25:27.952 --> 00:25:33.170
Give this problem
to this Paramchaitanya."

304
00:25:33.860 --> 00:25:37.579
And it works.

305
00:25:37.579 --> 00:25:46.898
Such tremendous things have happened
in this world just by bandhans

306
00:25:46.898 --> 00:25:55.694
that it is unbelievable
how these things are happening.

307
00:25:55.694 --> 00:26:03.593
Even, supposing you find,
there are so many murders,

308
00:26:03.593 --> 00:26:06.055
this thing has happened,
that thing has happened.

309
00:26:06.055 --> 00:26:11.810
This is also just to express
presence of Paramchaitanya.

310
00:26:11.810 --> 00:26:14.104
It's "Kruta".

311
00:26:14.104 --> 00:26:18.590
It's a working out, the way it works.

312
00:26:18.590 --> 00:26:21.776
"Kruta" means the one which is done.

313
00:26:21.776 --> 00:26:26.650
Then you start realising
that this power

314
00:26:26.650 --> 00:26:31.844
you can achieve through your Kundalini.

315
00:26:31.844 --> 00:26:36.334
So when your Kundalini rises,

316
00:26:36.334 --> 00:26:41.250
that is also a reflection of Adi Shakti,

317
00:26:41.250 --> 00:26:43.877
like we can say,
we see one part of moon,

318
00:26:43.877 --> 00:26:46.002
then another part we don't see.

319
00:26:46.002 --> 00:26:52.581
In the same way, this power,
when rises within you

320
00:26:52.581 --> 00:26:57.541
and touches this Paramchaitanya,

321
00:26:57.541 --> 00:27:00.789
then you become empowered by that.

322
00:27:05.006 --> 00:27:11.486
That's how you are Sahaja Yogis,
but you are not God.

323
00:27:11.486 --> 00:27:16.300
The incarnations can say,
"I am God."

324
00:27:16.300 --> 00:27:20.315
You are not incarnations,

325
00:27:20.315 --> 00:27:25.598
but none of the incarnations
have ever said

326
00:27:25.598 --> 00:27:31.340
that they are Adi Shakti, cannot.

327
00:27:31.910 --> 00:27:37.055
This power of Adi Shakti,
which we call as Paramchaitanya

328
00:27:37.247 --> 00:27:40.400
is the power that loves you,

329
00:27:40.400 --> 00:27:48.966
has complete control of the nature.
It understands you.

330
00:27:49.081 --> 00:27:52.216
It thinks, it knows everything.

331
00:27:52.273 --> 00:27:57.168
Everything about you, it knows.

332
00:27:57.168 --> 00:28:06.515
It works in every angle,
in every walk of your life.

333
00:28:06.515 --> 00:28:12.064
It is with you entirely as if,

334
00:28:12.064 --> 00:28:18.233
supposing you fall into a river
which is flowing fast

335
00:28:18.233 --> 00:28:26.252
and you cannot swim any more,
you cannot use your hands any more.

336
00:28:26.252 --> 00:28:28.177
You start flowing with it

337
00:28:28.278 --> 00:28:30.956
and then you realise
that flowing with it

338
00:28:30.956 --> 00:28:34.789
is a better thing
than to try to get out of it.

339
00:28:34.789 --> 00:28:37.865
You are just flowing with it.

340
00:28:37.865 --> 00:28:42.500
Just enjoying all the nature around you.

341
00:28:42.500 --> 00:28:44.162
You don't get drowned.

342
00:28:44.162 --> 00:28:46.928
On the contrary,
you feel you are elevated

343
00:28:46.928 --> 00:28:49.455
and you're flowing with it.

344
00:28:49.455 --> 00:28:52.941
Then you understand,
"What am I to do about something

345
00:28:52.941 --> 00:28:57.611
when it's done by Paramchaitanya for me?"

346
00:28:59.699 --> 00:29:03.983
But, credit it should be given
to your Kundalini

347
00:29:04.024 --> 00:29:06.267
which has worked it out,

348
00:29:06.267 --> 00:29:08.681
has put you onto that shore,

349
00:29:08.681 --> 00:29:16.422
has put you onto that beautiful,
heavenly Kingdom of God.

350
00:29:16.422 --> 00:29:21.250
Thus, you understand
there are two things that have happened,

351
00:29:21.250 --> 00:29:24.646
that first, your Mother,
your Kundalini which is within you,

352
00:29:24.646 --> 00:29:26.679
which is your own Mother,

353
00:29:26.679 --> 00:29:30.719
which has been with you throughout,
has given you this birth.

354
00:29:30.719 --> 00:29:34.348
And then it has taken to that power,

355
00:29:34.348 --> 00:29:42.277
which power you can use yourself.
You're empowered by that.

356
00:29:42.277 --> 00:29:45.020
You'll be amazed how this power helps.

357
00:29:45.020 --> 00:29:53.540
I mean, you see, I'm —
I shouldn't say that you can have all the powers.

358
00:29:53.540 --> 00:29:56.780
I shouldn't say that,
but today, you see,

359
00:29:56.780 --> 00:29:58.372
they were complaining about somebody.

360
00:29:58.372 --> 00:30:00.890
Immediately, I told them
the name of the person.

361
00:30:00.890 --> 00:30:03.010
Now, you'll say how I knew.

362
00:30:03.010 --> 00:30:07.708
But I just know.
That's all I can say. I just know.

363
00:30:07.708 --> 00:30:11.034
Supposing you are dealing with carpets, alright.

364
00:30:11.034 --> 00:30:14.033
So you know what pattern is this,
what pattern is that,

365
00:30:14.033 --> 00:30:17.105
from where it has come, everything.
You know.

366
00:30:17.105 --> 00:30:23.353
Isn't it?
If you are there you know everything.

367
00:30:23.353 --> 00:30:30.304
If this power is everywhere,
one has to know everything.

368
00:30:30.304 --> 00:30:35.280
The connection is such.
If you want to know, you can know anything.

369
00:30:35.280 --> 00:30:41.470
So, they have called also Buddha
as Sarvalokiteshwara,

370
00:30:41.470 --> 00:30:46.052
that He sees all the Lokas.

371
00:30:46.052 --> 00:30:50.061
How does He see?
Sarvalokiteshwara

372
00:30:50.061 --> 00:31:01.491
because His ego, what we call,
is the Parama-ego you can call it,

373
00:31:01.491 --> 00:31:06.508
the Mahatahamkara,
knows everything,

374
00:31:06.508 --> 00:31:11.042
while your ego doesn't know anything.

375
00:31:11.042 --> 00:31:21.896
Because it doesn't know anything,
you are enveloped by it.

376
00:31:21.896 --> 00:31:27.609
If he had known, if the ego had known
what is the truth,

377
00:31:27.609 --> 00:31:30.377
you'd be free person, absolutely free,

378
00:31:30.377 --> 00:31:34.366
but you don't want
to surrender your ego.

379
00:31:34.366 --> 00:31:41.975
You don't want to allow yourself
to flow into the river as Tao, He said it.

380
00:31:41.975 --> 00:31:44.392
No, you don't want to enjoy.

381
00:31:44.392 --> 00:31:49.599
You want to have your own speciality.

382
00:31:49.599 --> 00:31:56.840
Individuality is very different from having
a kind of an ego within yourself

383
00:31:56.840 --> 00:31:59.350
that I am this, I am that.

384
00:31:59.350 --> 00:32:03.359
So this differentiation must start.

385
00:32:03.359 --> 00:32:08.784
After realisation,
in the light of realisation,

386
00:32:08.784 --> 00:32:11.728
you should start seeing things.

387
00:32:11.728 --> 00:32:14.628
Now, the first and foremost thing

388
00:32:14.628 --> 00:32:17.622
is to tell your ego to sit down.

389
00:32:17.622 --> 00:32:20.599
"Keep quiet. You don't know anything."

390
00:32:20.599 --> 00:32:25.254
And also in the modern times
it's a big fashion,

391
00:32:25.269 --> 00:32:27.818
you ask somebody, "I don't know."

392
00:32:27.818 --> 00:32:32.384
You ask somebody, "What's your name?"
"I don't know."

393
00:32:32.384 --> 00:32:35.456
He doesn't even know his name.

394
00:32:35.456 --> 00:32:39.577
And to be stupid is a fashion.

395
00:32:39.577 --> 00:32:45.863
To show that you are very stupid,
they think they are showing

396
00:32:45.863 --> 00:32:49.929
they are very innocent.
It's not. It's stupidity.

397
00:32:49.929 --> 00:32:52.744
This stupidity
I don't know which animal has.

398
00:32:52.744 --> 00:32:55.934
Still I don't know what is the source of it.

399
00:32:55.934 --> 00:33:00.747
Still, I'll have to find out
who is the animal

400
00:33:00.747 --> 00:33:03.665
which has generated this stupidity in the —

401
00:33:03.665 --> 00:33:07.934
But I know one thing. It is our ego.

402
00:33:07.934 --> 00:33:14.006
Ego makes a person absolutely stupid.

403
00:33:14.006 --> 00:33:19.604
In Marathi, you see,
thank God language is so rich

404
00:33:19.604 --> 00:33:22.910
that anybody who starts showing off
his ego,

405
00:33:22.910 --> 00:33:25.828
they say he's climbing on a bush.

406
00:33:25.828 --> 00:33:30.126
There's a little bush
and he's climbing on that.

407
00:33:30.126 --> 00:33:43.963
All this ego comes through
your own so-called ideas, achievements.

408
00:33:43.963 --> 00:33:47.045
But what are these achievements?

409
00:33:47.045 --> 00:33:50.694
You don't know anything

410
00:33:53.220 --> 00:33:56.466
and this is what today I have to tell you

411
00:33:56.466 --> 00:34:02.755
that if anything is working out today
is your surrender of your ego.

412
00:34:02.755 --> 00:34:07.413
If you know how to surrender your ego,
you'll work it out.

413
00:34:07.413 --> 00:34:12.081
Another thing which surprises Me
sometimes, in the West specially,

414
00:34:12.081 --> 00:34:16.193
that I think the women are the power,
the Shakti,

415
00:34:16.193 --> 00:34:28.532
but in the West I find women
are not using Adi Shakti. No.

416
00:34:28.532 --> 00:34:39.535
Firstly, they are still very much possessed
by their emotions

417
00:34:39.535 --> 00:34:44.212
and by their ideas and things like that.

418
00:34:44.212 --> 00:34:47.163
One side is man, who is with the ego,

419
00:34:47.163 --> 00:34:53.302
but even women are very egoistical.
Very much. It's very difficult.

420
00:34:53.302 --> 00:35:01.345
For example, you marry some girl,
a western girl to somebody.

421
00:35:01.345 --> 00:35:06.580
She'll be very happy, jumping,
taking all the presents, congratulations,

422
00:35:06.580 --> 00:35:08.859
wearing all dress, everything.

423
00:35:08.859 --> 00:35:15.049
After ten days she'll come and say,
"Mother, I'm confused."

424
00:35:15.049 --> 00:35:19.540
"Confused? How?"
"I'm now confused."

425
00:35:19.540 --> 00:35:23.460
"You're confused now? Or before?"
"I'm now confused."

426
00:35:23.460 --> 00:35:26.190
"All right.
You return all your ornaments. Everything."

427
00:35:26.190 --> 00:35:29.426
"No, no, then let me think."

428
00:35:29.426 --> 00:35:34.398
This is not the level
of a Sahaja Yogini.

429
00:35:34.398 --> 00:35:42.248
Sahaja Yogini is the Shakti
and she has to take up challenges.

430
00:35:42.248 --> 00:35:45.700
"I'll show you. I'll do it better."

431
00:35:45.700 --> 00:35:49.715
On the contrary,
I find them extremely dominating.

432
00:35:49.715 --> 00:35:54.526
I'm amazed. Why should Shakti dominate?

433
00:35:54.526 --> 00:35:57.542
If she's Shakti, she'll not dominate.

434
00:35:57.555 --> 00:36:00.506
Those who are not will dominate.

435
00:36:00.506 --> 00:36:05.798
Like, you see, you go in India
to any collector's house,

436
00:36:05.798 --> 00:36:11.248
the collector would be humble,
but the constable would be dominating.

437
00:36:11.248 --> 00:36:18.610
In the same way, I find this domination
business is very common

438
00:36:18.610 --> 00:36:27.370
and also a kind of a temperament
like a nun.

439
00:36:27.370 --> 00:36:33.011
They'll dress up like a nun,
behave like a nun, they won't smile.

440
00:36:33.011 --> 00:36:36.980
What is it?
Are you Sahaj Yoginis or what are you?

441
00:36:36.980 --> 00:36:39.662
Are you nuns?
Then better join nunnery.

442
00:36:39.662 --> 00:36:45.369
Why I'm telling you, we're talking
about Adi Shakti so I'm talking about Shakti.

443
00:36:45.369 --> 00:36:48.026
How the Shakti has to come up?

444
00:36:48.026 --> 00:36:53.168
I was surprised that women
were not spreading Sahaja Yoga.

445
00:36:53.168 --> 00:36:56.995
Somebody told me that leaders
don't want women to spread Sahaja Yoga.

446
00:36:56.995 --> 00:37:01.070
I said, "It's wrong.
If the leaders say that, it's not proper."

447
00:37:01.070 --> 00:37:07.780
But first of all,
the Sahaja Yoginis have to be real

448
00:37:07.780 --> 00:37:09.959
Sahaja Yoginis

449
00:37:09.959 --> 00:37:13.778
because so far I have seen anyone —

450
00:37:13.778 --> 00:37:18.651
you try to give any lady,
try to give her the position of a leader,

451
00:37:18.651 --> 00:37:25.942
she just finishes off the people.
Not all, but some.

452
00:37:25.942 --> 00:37:36.860
Now, the duty of a Sahaja Yogini
is to develop herself

453
00:37:36.860 --> 00:37:44.513
through meditation,
through understanding oneself

454
00:37:44.513 --> 00:37:49.291
and through self-esteem that,
"I am a Sahaja Yogini.

455
00:37:49.291 --> 00:37:55.247
I am the one who is Shakti.
I'm the potential of that."

456
00:37:55.247 --> 00:37:58.700
I'm the potential myself.
What do I do? Nothing.

457
00:37:58.700 --> 00:38:02.060
I didn't erect this.
I didn't put this on, nothing of the kind.

458
00:38:02.060 --> 00:38:09.535
I'm nicely sitting here talking.
But potential I am.

459
00:38:09.535 --> 00:38:12.326
"Am I the potential?"

460
00:38:12.326 --> 00:38:17.569
This is what the Sahaja Yoginis
have to decide.

461
00:38:17.569 --> 00:38:23.759
Otherwise, they are possessed,
they are daydreaming,

462
00:38:23.759 --> 00:38:27.733
thinking no end of themselves.
It's very difficult.

463
00:38:27.733 --> 00:38:34.265
I want some nice Sahaja Yoginis
to be the leaders — I really want —

464
00:38:34.265 --> 00:38:41.021
but as soon as they become leader,
they are on a horse, running so fast.

465
00:38:41.021 --> 00:38:44.495
So humble down yourself.

466
00:38:44.495 --> 00:38:51.472
Unless and until there is a big space
in the pitcher,

467
00:38:51.472 --> 00:38:53.954
what water can flow into it?

468
00:38:53.954 --> 00:38:56.723
Have a very large heart.

469
00:38:56.723 --> 00:39:01.064
Anybody comes to your house,
you don't like it,

470
00:39:01.064 --> 00:39:05.186
don't want to do anything
for other Sahaja Yogis,

471
00:39:05.186 --> 00:39:06.888
looking after them.

472
00:39:06.888 --> 00:39:12.283
It is, really, I say again and again,
in the West

473
00:39:12.283 --> 00:39:15.672
that women have to take up Shakti
into themselves

474
00:39:15.672 --> 00:39:17.743
and Shakti doesn't mean
dominate your husband

475
00:39:17.743 --> 00:39:19.010
and make a fool out of him.

476
00:39:19.010 --> 00:39:23.059
No, it means give him powers.

477
00:39:23.059 --> 00:39:27.475
You are the supplier of power
of the whole family

478
00:39:27.475 --> 00:39:30.396
and this is our family.

479
00:39:30.396 --> 00:39:32.111
All this is my family.

480
00:39:32.111 --> 00:39:37.210
I am so concerned about everyone,
even the little thing I am bothered about.

481
00:39:37.210 --> 00:39:42.050
I am never satisfied that,
"I have done my job now

482
00:39:42.050 --> 00:39:47.898
and now tonight I'll go off to sleep
and I'll not think of anyone." Never.

483
00:39:47.898 --> 00:39:50.945
Concerned about this
and concerned about that —

484
00:39:50.945 --> 00:39:55.211
all the time it's flowing, this power,

485
00:39:55.211 --> 00:40:02.890
and My concern is powerful,
that works, because My concern is genuine.

486
00:40:02.890 --> 00:40:06.253
I'm not concerned about Myself, never.

487
00:40:06.253 --> 00:40:11.150
You'll be amazed when I see all these women
doing all kinds of things

488
00:40:11.150 --> 00:40:13.893
to preserve themselves, I am surprised.

489
00:40:13.930 --> 00:40:18.388
What is needed is the concern.

490
00:40:18.388 --> 00:40:21.535
And once you develop that concern —

491
00:40:21.535 --> 00:40:26.762
a genuine, loving, compassionate concern
about others.

492
00:40:26.762 --> 00:40:30.820
Even about children,
I've seen that they never look after

493
00:40:30.820 --> 00:40:34.270
each other's children.
They never help others.

494
00:40:34.270 --> 00:40:37.055
Somebody had to go
for taking out the tooth.

495
00:40:37.094 --> 00:40:39.094
She had to carry the child with her.

496
00:40:39.094 --> 00:40:41.564
I mean this is too much.

497
00:40:41.564 --> 00:40:47.838
If you do not have concern,
then you will not have collective mind,

498
00:40:47.868 --> 00:40:49.953
you'll not have the collective power

499
00:40:49.953 --> 00:40:55.050
and is important that you all
should try to be very collective,

500
00:40:55.123 --> 00:40:56.670
look after each other's.

501
00:40:56.670 --> 00:40:58.959
Now, I shouldn't say this.

502
00:40:58.959 --> 00:41:01.289
I was going to tell to Cabella ladies,

503
00:41:01.289 --> 00:41:04.522
that this Cabella is an ashram

504
00:41:04.522 --> 00:41:06.850
and those people who come
from other ashrams,

505
00:41:06.850 --> 00:41:09.970
even from Australia are surprised that,

506
00:41:09.970 --> 00:41:12.520
"They are all living here
just like a hotel.

507
00:41:12.520 --> 00:41:16.852
They're paying for it.
We all pay, but we have gardens.

508
00:41:16.852 --> 00:41:19.711
We look after the gardens.
We look after the outside.

509
00:41:19.747 --> 00:41:26.051
Here nobody is bothered.
They're using everything — not bothered."

510
00:41:26.051 --> 00:41:31.064
Surprisingly, why, when I am living here
they are like this.

511
00:41:31.064 --> 00:41:35.415
You go to any place in Australia,
you go to America, anywhere,

512
00:41:35.415 --> 00:41:39.315
wherever there is an ashram,
they all work on Sundays,

513
00:41:39.315 --> 00:41:40.364
they look after.

514
00:41:40.364 --> 00:41:42.694
Here I have not seen,
they all disappear.

515
00:41:42.694 --> 00:41:45.269
This is your ashram.

516
00:41:45.269 --> 00:41:46.670
You are staying here

517
00:41:46.670 --> 00:41:49.644
and is now — today I had to tell this

518
00:41:49.644 --> 00:41:56.407
because I feel that Sahaja Yoga
is missing out itself on their Shaktis.

519
00:41:56.407 --> 00:42:00.447
Some of them do not know
how to smile even,

520
00:42:00.447 --> 00:42:03.405
and some of them
are extremely dominating.

521
00:42:03.405 --> 00:42:07.013
I have to tell you this
because you are so important.

522
00:42:07.013 --> 00:42:10.383
But for Me, no man
would have done this job.

523
00:42:10.383 --> 00:42:13.270
No man incarnation
would have done this job.

524
00:42:13.270 --> 00:42:16.384
Nice, they get crucified at a young age.

525
00:42:16.384 --> 00:42:20.340
Very nice, get crucified at such a young age,

526
00:42:20.340 --> 00:42:23.170
then another one takes to poison,

527
00:42:23.170 --> 00:42:26.544
another one is killed by somebody.

528
00:42:26.544 --> 00:42:29.105
It's like that.
They all died very young.

529
00:42:29.105 --> 00:42:31.974
Nobody wanted to do this work.

530
00:42:33.870 --> 00:42:37.025
I mean. They got fed up. They got fed up.

531
00:42:37.025 --> 00:42:41.343
We had Gyaneshwara who went into Samadhi
at the age of twenty-three years.

532
00:42:41.353 --> 00:42:42.577
Can you imagine?

533
00:42:42.577 --> 00:42:45.231
He must have been fed up
with the people.

534
00:42:45.231 --> 00:42:49.971
Now, it is for you people, the ladies,

535
00:42:49.971 --> 00:42:53.346
to have that patience of your Mother,

536
00:42:53.346 --> 00:42:55.211
that affection, that love

537
00:42:55.211 --> 00:42:59.477
and then you will see
how your Shakti will work out.

538
00:42:59.477 --> 00:43:03.989
I, again and again,
always have talked about this

539
00:43:03.989 --> 00:43:11.197
and, at Adi Shakti point, I have to say
you are in your family like a Shakti.

540
00:43:11.197 --> 00:43:15.635
And you have to be wise,
you have to be sensible,

541
00:43:15.635 --> 00:43:17.390
you have to understand your husband,

542
00:43:17.390 --> 00:43:20.639
you have to understand your children,
you have to have patience.

543
00:43:20.639 --> 00:43:23.791
On the contrary, they spoil their children.

544
00:43:23.791 --> 00:43:26.660
That is to be understood,

545
00:43:26.660 --> 00:43:30.938
that you must know first
what is good for their benevolence.

546
00:43:30.938 --> 00:43:35.510
Today, for example, if I say the children,

547
00:43:35.510 --> 00:43:38.751
if they go to a school,
they should not be removed.

548
00:43:38.751 --> 00:43:41.295
It is for their benevolence.

549
00:43:41.295 --> 00:43:43.994
What are the people going to gain out of it?

550
00:43:43.994 --> 00:43:48.430
So somebody says, "No."
All right, get out.

551
00:43:48.430 --> 00:43:51.090
What can you do?

552
00:43:51.090 --> 00:43:58.645
Such attachment to your own children
shows you are a powerless person.

553
00:43:58.645 --> 00:44:01.333
You must love all the children.

554
00:44:01.333 --> 00:44:03.734
You must look after all the children.

555
00:44:03.734 --> 00:44:09.113
You must enjoy all the children,
take interest in them.

556
00:44:09.113 --> 00:44:12.696
But what I find,
that they're only interested

557
00:44:12.696 --> 00:44:15.160
in their own children.

558
00:44:15.160 --> 00:44:20.867
We are a joint family, we should say.
We all live together.

559
00:44:20.867 --> 00:44:24.498
We have to share everything.

560
00:44:24.498 --> 00:44:28.743
It is something I can't understand.

561
00:44:28.743 --> 00:44:33.932
Say, in India, if you see
5, 6 children,

562
00:44:33.932 --> 00:44:37.071
all the girls will run after them.

563
00:44:37.071 --> 00:44:40.070
All the women will look after them.

564
00:44:40.070 --> 00:44:42.645
I mean, it's such a pleasure to them,
to see any children,

565
00:44:42.645 --> 00:44:45.434
just to look after them.

566
00:44:45.434 --> 00:44:52.510
But this kind of insensitivity
to your collective behaviour

567
00:44:52.510 --> 00:44:56.092
is going to also spoil your children.

568
00:44:56.092 --> 00:45:00.559
So, what you're going to transmit
to the whole world

569
00:45:00.559 --> 00:45:06.386
is this Sahaj living.

570
00:45:06.386 --> 00:45:09.456
And the women make the society.

571
00:45:09.456 --> 00:45:13.367
If Indian society is good,
the credit goes to the Indian women

572
00:45:13.367 --> 00:45:15.102
and to their wisdom.

573
00:45:15.102 --> 00:45:17.337
Our men are stupid in India.

574
00:45:17.337 --> 00:45:20.357
They have spoiled politics,
economics, everything,

575
00:45:20.357 --> 00:45:25.031
but society is still maintained

576
00:45:25.031 --> 00:45:30.698
and they are very, very still,
say, on the right path.

577
00:45:30.698 --> 00:45:34.588
This only comes
because of the wisdom of the women.

578
00:45:34.588 --> 00:45:38.561
If the women are busy dressing up
for hours together,

579
00:45:38.561 --> 00:45:43.695
thinking about their clothes,
what they are going to wear — finished.

580
00:45:47.719 --> 00:45:56.301
This is a day of worshipping
the Kundalini, who is the Mother.

581
00:45:56.301 --> 00:46:01.633
She is the Mother and you are the Mother.

582
00:46:01.633 --> 00:46:04.728
You must know each and everything
about your child.

583
00:46:04.728 --> 00:46:08.600
Somebody comes and tells me,
"My child is now a drug addict."

584
00:46:08.600 --> 00:46:10.507
How can it be possible?

585
00:46:10.507 --> 00:46:13.816
In India children don't become
drug addicts

586
00:46:13.850 --> 00:46:18.461
because all the time the mother is on
their head like a hawk.

587
00:46:18.461 --> 00:46:21.316
She knows where he goes,
what he does.

588
00:46:21.316 --> 00:46:26.534
She loves, but she knows where he goes.

589
00:46:26.534 --> 00:46:29.060
I mean, even when we were in college,

590
00:46:29.060 --> 00:46:32.375
even when I'm married,
if I went home my mother would ask,

591
00:46:32.375 --> 00:46:33.549
"Where did you go?"

592
00:46:34.820 --> 00:46:36.575
We dare not say anything.

593
00:46:36.575 --> 00:46:40.100
"Come back by six,"
even when we are married.

594
00:46:42.852 --> 00:46:45.553
And we are supposed to tell her.

595
00:46:45.553 --> 00:46:48.365
That's what's the mother's work —

596
00:46:48.365 --> 00:46:51.507
the child, where he goes,
what does he do.

597
00:46:51.507 --> 00:46:53.870
And then to say children
doesn't listen to you.

598
00:46:53.870 --> 00:46:59.465
Because — why the children don't listen?
Because you do not discipline them.

599
00:46:59.465 --> 00:47:04.092
Here the atmosphere is very bad, agreed,

600
00:47:04.092 --> 00:47:08.459
and the children are very bad, agreed.
Everything is there, agreed.

601
00:47:08.459 --> 00:47:12.798
But if you are a strong mother
in your love,

602
00:47:12.798 --> 00:47:15.080
your children will not go.

603
00:47:15.080 --> 00:47:20.343
See, even now, as you know that
all the time they are,

604
00:47:20.343 --> 00:47:22.912
all these leaders
are hovering around Me.

605
00:47:22.912 --> 00:47:26.526
And what is there?
I have no honey with Me or anything.

606
00:47:26.526 --> 00:47:31.830
They are just sitting there,
just sitting next to Me, all the leaders.

607
00:47:31.830 --> 00:47:34.654
But this is after realisation,

608
00:47:34.654 --> 00:47:40.818
but even all my nephews, you see,
they would all come and sit next to Me,

609
00:47:40.818 --> 00:47:46.077
all my daughter-in-laws
they would all sit next to Me.

610
00:47:46.980 --> 00:47:48.110
They would not leave Me

611
00:47:48.110 --> 00:47:50.557
and people used to ask them,
"What's wrong with you?

612
00:47:50.557 --> 00:47:54.259
You're all the time sticking
onto your aunt. What is it?"

613
00:47:54.259 --> 00:47:56.404
The concern.

614
00:47:57.900 --> 00:48:00.747
And they understand
it is for their benevolence

615
00:48:00.747 --> 00:48:02.876
that you are telling them,

616
00:48:03.821 --> 00:48:06.100
but yourself should be all right.

617
00:48:09.052 --> 00:48:14.021
As a mother, one has to be tolerant,
one has to understand,

618
00:48:14.021 --> 00:48:16.618
but when you have to tell them,
you have to tell them.

619
00:48:17.776 --> 00:48:21.645
If you think,
you can tell them sharply

620
00:48:21.645 --> 00:48:23.807
or maybe in a proper way,

621
00:48:23.807 --> 00:48:27.227
but the child should know
that you love the child

622
00:48:27.227 --> 00:48:33.730
and that you love all the children.
It is very subtle.

623
00:48:34.828 --> 00:48:39.661
Like I've seen,
once I took a child of one Sahaja Yogi

624
00:48:39.661 --> 00:48:41.345
with Me to the market

625
00:48:41.345 --> 00:48:45.373
and he was asking,
"I'll buy this. I'll buy that. I'll buy that."

626
00:48:45.373 --> 00:48:47.001
Everything he wanted to buy.

627
00:48:47.001 --> 00:48:49.650
I was wondering what is wrong
with this boy.

628
00:48:49.650 --> 00:48:54.127
But, say, if I take
my own grandchildren, they wouldn't buy. Nothing.

629
00:48:54.127 --> 00:48:57.033
Even if you want to buy
two pairs of shoes.

630
00:48:57.033 --> 00:48:58.629
"No, no, no, one is sufficient.

631
00:48:58.629 --> 00:49:00.071
If this will be spoiled, all right."

632
00:49:00.090 --> 00:49:01.614
They'll never ask for anything.

633
00:49:01.614 --> 00:49:09.495
It is a kind of self-esteem.
They don't want anything.

634
00:49:09.495 --> 00:49:11.247
Same with the wives.

635
00:49:11.247 --> 00:49:16.820
Wives never ask for anything from them.
No, nothing. Nothing we want.

636
00:49:16.820 --> 00:49:21.030
The husband will go on asking,
"Please ask for something.

637
00:49:21.030 --> 00:49:24.867
Ask for something."
"No. We don't want anything."

638
00:49:24.867 --> 00:49:28.576
That is going to be
a Sahaja Yogini mother

639
00:49:28.576 --> 00:49:31.645
and a wife and a Shakti.

640
00:49:31.645 --> 00:49:39.093
She has no demands.
Nothing she's asking for.

641
00:49:39.093 --> 00:49:42.559
The one who is a giver,
what is she going to ask?

642
00:49:44.625 --> 00:49:47.609
The one who is a supplier,
what is she going to ask?

643
00:49:50.699 --> 00:49:55.387
So, I feel sometimes
that the left side, or the women's side,

644
00:49:55.387 --> 00:50:02.471
in Sahaja Yoga is a little bit going down
and they have to come up.

645
00:50:02.471 --> 00:50:05.967
First meditation, respect of Mother,

646
00:50:05.967 --> 00:50:09.502
teaching the children
how to work out Sahaja Yoga,

647
00:50:09.502 --> 00:50:11.717
talking to them about Sahaja Yoga

648
00:50:11.717 --> 00:50:19.708
and not only about food,
of cleanliness,

649
00:50:19.708 --> 00:50:24.065
of being nice to others,
how to share things

650
00:50:26.830 --> 00:50:33.664
and telling children
about good stories that you have heard,

651
00:50:33.664 --> 00:50:38.355
telling them what is dharma,
talking to them, having a rapport.

652
00:50:40.018 --> 00:50:44.779
This is what you have to understand
to make Sahaja Yoga very strong.

653
00:50:46.488 --> 00:50:50.219
You are the Shakti of Sahaja Yoga,
take it from Me,

654
00:50:50.219 --> 00:50:53.875
and you have to work it out that way,

655
00:50:53.875 --> 00:50:57.981
instead of worrying
about small, small things.

656
00:50:57.981 --> 00:51:01.284
Sometimes I receive letters
from the ladies

657
00:51:01.284 --> 00:51:04.161
is something —
really it pains Me.

658
00:51:04.705 --> 00:51:07.129
Can't understand
how they are Sahaj Yogis.

659
00:51:12.730 --> 00:51:19.545
Our whole system of Sahaj
has to be a model system,

660
00:51:19.547 --> 00:51:23.905
that others should see and understand

661
00:51:23.905 --> 00:51:29.691
that what we have achieved
in our day-to-day life.

662
00:51:29.691 --> 00:51:35.641
Adi Shakti works in day-to-day life,
the smallest things to the highest.

663
00:51:37.378 --> 00:51:39.606
And all the time you have to learn.

664
00:51:39.606 --> 00:51:41.361
All the time you have to learn,

665
00:51:41.361 --> 00:51:43.799
whether you are a leader
or not a leader.

666
00:51:43.799 --> 00:51:47.427
All the time you must know
what you have to know.

667
00:51:47.427 --> 00:51:50.608
"I have not known this.
I have not known that."

668
00:51:50.608 --> 00:51:56.875
Unless and until you develop that kind
of an attitude that "I have to learn,"

669
00:51:56.875 --> 00:52:00.764
that humble attitude, that humility —

670
00:52:00.764 --> 00:52:04.525
"I have to learn, I have to learn,
still I have to learn" —

671
00:52:04.525 --> 00:52:06.796
this ego will never come.

672
00:52:06.796 --> 00:52:10.110
Because of this ego
you are satisfied with yourself.

673
00:52:10.110 --> 00:52:12.580
That's the sign of an ego.

674
00:52:12.580 --> 00:52:15.597
You don't know how much
you are torturing others,

675
00:52:15.597 --> 00:52:17.315
what you are destroying, nothing,

676
00:52:17.381 --> 00:52:20.714
but you feel extremely happy
with yourself.

677
00:52:24.958 --> 00:52:32.273
Such a happy-go-lucky personality
sometimes is living on air.

678
00:52:35.195 --> 00:52:38.008
"What have I done today
for somebody else?

679
00:52:39.956 --> 00:52:42.369
How have I talked to somebody else?

680
00:52:42.369 --> 00:52:45.036
What have I given to somebody else?"

681
00:52:46.024 --> 00:52:48.567
I need not give you presents.
There's nothing.

682
00:52:48.567 --> 00:52:50.377
Why should I give you presents?

683
00:52:50.387 --> 00:52:54.250
But I give you presents
because of my own satisfaction.

684
00:52:55.927 --> 00:53:00.271
And if I take presents from you,
it is for your own satisfaction.

685
00:53:01.784 --> 00:53:06.301
So, what we have to do
in what we find satisfaction.

686
00:53:07.694 --> 00:53:12.706
What do you find satisfaction in?
Just think about it.

687
00:53:12.706 --> 00:53:15.357
What do we find satisfaction in?

688
00:53:15.357 --> 00:53:19.208
"My house should be all right.
My husband should be all right.

689
00:53:19.208 --> 00:53:23.561
My children should be all right."
My, my, my.

690
00:53:26.246 --> 00:53:29.806
Unless and until this "my"
shifts to another person,

691
00:53:30.072 --> 00:53:35.903
you are still in the realm of Maya.

692
00:53:41.148 --> 00:53:49.479
You have to learn this,
is to think every day or write —

693
00:53:49.479 --> 00:53:51.715
all of you should write diaries,

694
00:53:51.715 --> 00:53:57.306
"What have I done for others?
What have I said to others?

695
00:53:59.911 --> 00:54:05.094
What will make or please
another person?"

696
00:54:07.394 --> 00:54:13.223
Small, small things can make
the life so beautiful.

697
00:54:13.223 --> 00:54:18.145
And also very big things
there are for you.

698
00:54:18.368 --> 00:54:21.850
If you do not think
you are very big,

699
00:54:21.850 --> 00:54:25.616
all these big things are also for you.

700
00:54:29.397 --> 00:54:35.039
It's like this —
this whole sky can be covered

701
00:54:35.039 --> 00:54:36.755
by one leaf.

702
00:54:36.755 --> 00:54:46.143
If you see the leaf against the sky,
the leaf shows its existence.

703
00:54:47.753 --> 00:54:53.057
In the same way,
this whole vision of Sahaja Yoga

704
00:54:54.898 --> 00:55:02.703
can be completely covered
by one person who stands

705
00:55:02.703 --> 00:55:08.019
with this great expanse,

706
00:55:09.740 --> 00:55:13.309
one person here and one person there.

707
00:55:13.309 --> 00:55:16.301
It's so remarkable.

708
00:55:16.301 --> 00:55:18.330
With such a lot of Sahaj Yoga,

709
00:55:18.330 --> 00:55:22.035
there are people
who are here, there and there.

710
00:55:22.035 --> 00:55:27.449
So remarkable that if you take
their names also,

711
00:55:27.449 --> 00:55:35.345
I just feel I am drenched
into the Ocean of Joy.

712
00:55:35.345 --> 00:55:40.938
Only one person,
then what about you?

713
00:55:43.669 --> 00:55:46.060
Why can't we do that?

714
00:55:46.060 --> 00:55:50.406
When Adi Shakti is with you, reflected,

715
00:55:50.412 --> 00:55:57.535
when all Her Powers are with you,
how much we can do?

716
00:55:57.535 --> 00:56:03.169
In this expanse of My Vision,

717
00:56:03.169 --> 00:56:15.193
I want to have more and more people
who will be of some visions themselves,

718
00:56:16.661 --> 00:56:20.928
but not small people
who just think of their children,

719
00:56:20.928 --> 00:56:23.376
think of food. No, no,
they are not wanted.

720
00:56:23.376 --> 00:56:26.260
Useless, they will all drop out.

721
00:56:31.636 --> 00:56:38.574
I hope you have understood
where you are, what you have.

722
00:56:38.574 --> 00:56:43.346
What is created within you
is this Kundalini

723
00:56:43.346 --> 00:56:45.973
which has given you
all the knowledge, everything,

724
00:56:45.973 --> 00:56:50.020
but there are so many, I know,
they don't even know what is this chakra —

725
00:56:50.020 --> 00:56:53.926
they don't know — I mean,
going to that limit of ignorance.

726
00:56:53.926 --> 00:56:56.223
You have to know all these things.

727
00:56:57.543 --> 00:56:59.886
You have to understand what is it

728
00:57:02.531 --> 00:57:10.500
because this is for you,
all for you, all this knowledge.

729
00:57:10.500 --> 00:57:16.227
And the greatest of all is the faith,

730
00:57:16.227 --> 00:57:20.532
not a faith which is blind
but enlightened faith

731
00:57:20.532 --> 00:57:24.208
that you are now one
with that Divine Power.

732
00:57:26.146 --> 00:57:29.082
This should really settle you completely.

733
00:57:30.887 --> 00:57:34.410
This, I think, is one of the most
important pujas

734
00:57:34.826 --> 00:57:41.052
because, so far, Guru Pujas have been there

735
00:57:41.088 --> 00:57:43.905
— so many people were worshipped
as gurus —

736
00:57:43.905 --> 00:57:48.474
or maybe My Birthday,
as you think it to be. It's all right.

737
00:57:48.474 --> 00:57:54.887
But, I think to understand
your own powers of Kundalini

738
00:57:54.887 --> 00:57:59.578
and your powers
that are available to you,

739
00:57:59.578 --> 00:58:05.009
through the working
of Paramchaitanya, is very important.

740
00:58:05.009 --> 00:58:08.520
That will give you confidence,
that'll give you compassion,

741
00:58:08.520 --> 00:58:10.801
that will give you a vision

742
00:58:10.806 --> 00:58:14.196
and that will make you
a very great personality,

743
00:58:14.196 --> 00:58:15.750
a very great personality.

744
00:58:17.268 --> 00:58:21.166
What was George Washington?
They said he was great.

745
00:58:21.166 --> 00:58:24.480
Or what was Abraham Lincoln?
He was great.

746
00:58:24.480 --> 00:58:27.940
But you are all having
your Self-realisation.

747
00:58:30.026 --> 00:58:35.186
You have to think of the whole universe,
the whole expanse.

748
00:58:35.186 --> 00:58:38.173
Unless and until that brain
develops in you,

749
00:58:38.173 --> 00:58:41.396
I'm sure, very sure

750
00:58:41.396 --> 00:58:47.230
that the progress of Sahaja Yoga,
within and without, will be less.

751
00:58:47.230 --> 00:58:49.500
So understand
these powers are with you.

752
00:58:49.500 --> 00:58:53.307
You have to utilise them
with humility.

753
00:58:54.176 --> 00:58:57.640
May God bless you all.

754
00:59:12.660 --> 00:59:18.507
Now first of all we'll have to do
one Ganesha puja also,

755
00:59:18.507 --> 00:59:22.240
and then the Devi puja.
